WEBVTT

03:13.800 --> 03:16.600
They say big dreams
are sold in some cities.

03:17.200 --> 03:19.880
Because the city and its monotonous
life needs the vision and color

03:20.000 --> 03:22.840
of a beautiful dream to make itself big.

03:24.120 --> 03:25.680
My city is somewhat similar.

03:25.760 --> 03:29.920
Where I lived the dream of
becoming a super model.

03:30.360 --> 03:32.640
I, Meghna Mathur...

03:33.240 --> 03:36.120
have dreams bigger than this city.

03:39.480 --> 03:41.720
Since you were tired of
eating the potato pancakes

03:41.840 --> 03:43.760
I made radish pancakes for you.

03:43.840 --> 03:45.320
-Mom, this has a lot of butter.
-Have it.

03:45.760 --> 03:47.680
I told you I am on a diet.

03:47.920 --> 03:48.960
Having one won't make a difference.

03:49.040 --> 03:50.880
Of course, it will.
I have to lose two kilos.

03:54.200 --> 03:55.800
I got my portfolio yesterday.

03:58.840 --> 04:02.440
I was thinking of leaving
for Mumbai on Monday.

04:04.320 --> 04:08.520
That reminds me, I have
spoken to Mehra Associates.

04:09.400 --> 04:11.640
They have agreed on an
internship with them

04:11.720 --> 04:13.840
while you finish your chartered
accountants course.

04:13.920 --> 04:15.200
In fact, you can join them on Monday.

04:15.320 --> 04:17.040
Papa, you didn't hear me.

04:19.200 --> 04:20.640
I want to go to Mumbai...

04:21.600 --> 04:22.600
to become a model.

04:24.600 --> 04:26.160
I don't want to do any internship.

04:28.240 --> 04:32.160
Meghna, I've told you earlier.

04:33.720 --> 04:34.760
Never mind.

04:35.160 --> 04:38.240
Listen, dreaming isn't bad but--

04:38.320 --> 04:39.320
But what, Papa?

04:40.880 --> 04:42.720
Do I've to dream according to you?

04:44.120 --> 04:45.680
Can't I have my own dreams?

04:48.680 --> 04:49.760
I have decided.

04:51.960 --> 04:53.120
I want to go to Mumbai.

04:53.920 --> 04:57.840
In that case, there is
nothing left to discuss.

04:58.640 --> 04:59.800
Do as you wish.

05:00.720 --> 05:02.120
But don't expect anything from me.

05:02.200 --> 05:03.680
I was expecting for
a little encouragement but--

05:03.800 --> 05:05.440
Encouragement for what?

05:08.480 --> 05:13.920
You lost your mind after
winning that local beauty pageant.

05:18.480 --> 05:20.600
It was my fault.

05:24.280 --> 05:25.560
"Want to be a model!"

05:34.960 --> 05:38.200
Though I have spoken to
Brother Baldev...

05:38.280 --> 05:40.440
call me as soon as you reach.

05:42.920 --> 05:44.280
Papa...

05:49.720 --> 05:53.640
Don't worry, dear.
Everything will be alright.

05:54.960 --> 05:55.960
Give me a hug.

05:59.600 --> 06:02.360
You were so young during
Brother Kuldeep's wedding.

06:03.800 --> 06:06.720
Divya was really happy ever since
she learnt you were coming.

06:07.000 --> 06:07.840
Sister...

06:07.920 --> 06:09.760
Mom was mentioning
that you are going to be a model.

06:11.000 --> 06:14.600
Mom, it would be fun to watch
her on television.

06:14.680 --> 06:15.680
Divya...

06:17.080 --> 06:19.760
Come, Meghna.
I will take you to your room.

06:19.840 --> 06:20.760
Of course.

06:24.640 --> 06:26.120
This is Divya's room.

06:27.600 --> 06:29.520
You will have to share it with her.

06:29.600 --> 06:30.560
No problem.

06:30.920 --> 06:31.960
It's a little small...

06:32.520 --> 06:34.760
but you won't be here for long.

06:34.840 --> 06:37.720
Maybe a month, until I get work.

06:37.800 --> 06:41.160
Alright. You can freshen up.
Meanwhile, I will serve breakfast.

07:03.200 --> 07:04.480
No, it's in the evening.

07:20.920 --> 07:22.560
I'm sorry, I'm late.
But what could I do?

07:22.720 --> 07:24.400
Vinay wouldn't let me go.

07:29.240 --> 07:31.200
This evening we have to
do fittings for Duggu.

07:32.520 --> 07:33.320
Duggu?

07:33.640 --> 07:35.480
Duggu! Hrithik!

07:39.720 --> 07:40.560
I'm okay.

07:40.760 --> 07:43.520
You know, when I saw you in that silly
beauty contest in Chandigarh...

07:47.920 --> 07:49.840
I'm here because you
were confident about me.

07:50.200 --> 07:51.800
Now everything depends on you.

07:54.320 --> 07:55.600
-Do you have your pictures?
-Yes, of course!

08:03.280 --> 08:04.280
What's the matter?

08:13.640 --> 08:14.680
Who are you looking for?

08:16.920 --> 08:17.920
Here?

08:18.480 --> 08:19.400
Shomu.

08:21.440 --> 08:23.480
A Godmother to the newcomers.

08:25.000 --> 08:26.000
Hey! What man!

08:26.440 --> 08:28.120
Have you ever traveled by
plane before?

08:28.440 --> 08:29.960
I'm sending you to a foreign location.

08:30.040 --> 08:31.320
So what if the role is small?

08:31.600 --> 08:32.799
You will suffer one day.

08:32.919 --> 08:35.400
And Shweta, you have a two day job.

08:35.720 --> 08:38.720
No one gives more than 25,000 rupees
for a Punjabi dance number.

08:39.520 --> 08:42.080
I would have done it,
if I were taller.

08:42.600 --> 08:43.880
Ma'am, you are being called inside.

08:44.280 --> 08:45.280
Who is it?

08:52.400 --> 08:53.360
Are you new?

08:53.440 --> 08:55.040
-Are you from the North?
-Yes.

08:55.600 --> 08:56.600
What's your size?

08:59.640 --> 09:01.120
Listen, I am not interested.

09:01.360 --> 09:04.240
It's the client who wants to know.

09:05.680 --> 09:07.480
Hey! I was just about to call you.

09:07.640 --> 09:10.000
I'm sending a girl for the catalogue.
Check her out.

09:10.080 --> 09:11.120
What is your name?

09:11.360 --> 09:12.960
Meghna... Meghna Mathur.

09:13.040 --> 09:14.560
Her name is Meghna Mathur.

09:15.360 --> 09:16.360
Bye.

09:16.960 --> 09:18.880
Okay, listen. You have
an audition tomorrow.

09:19.240 --> 09:21.800
B 409, Adarsh Nagar.
Be there at eleven o'clock.

09:21.880 --> 09:22.920
Take the number from this chick.

09:23.120 --> 09:23.960
Chick?

09:24.040 --> 09:25.040
An audition tomorrow?

09:25.120 --> 09:26.520
Yes. And listen, if it works

09:26.600 --> 09:29.080
I'll take a twenty per cent cut.
Is that clear?

09:29.160 --> 09:30.360
Okay.

09:34.800 --> 09:36.160
Stop here. I think this is the place.

09:41.920 --> 09:42.920
How much is the bill?

09:43.320 --> 09:44.320
Fifteen rupees.

09:46.120 --> 09:47.120
Take this.

09:55.000 --> 09:56.720
I recently did two advertisements.

09:57.000 --> 09:58.040
What about you?

09:58.800 --> 09:59.840
I'm an air hostess.

10:00.120 --> 10:02.360
I got bored of serving people.

10:02.800 --> 10:04.520
So now I want to be a model.

10:04.600 --> 10:05.680
Do you have a problem with that?

10:06.360 --> 10:08.200
-No.
-Then stop bothering me.

10:08.440 --> 10:09.800
It is a soap commercial, right?

10:09.880 --> 10:10.880
Alright, I will be there.

10:11.440 --> 10:12.720
I am at Adarsh Nagar right now.

10:12.880 --> 10:14.320
I will be at Famous Studios in an hour.

10:26.360 --> 10:27.360
Yes.

10:27.840 --> 10:28.840
Are you auditioning for the first time?

10:30.120 --> 10:31.200
How did you guess?

10:32.160 --> 10:34.320
Only novices walk around
with their portfolio.

10:35.360 --> 10:38.920
Seasoned models, like us,
send it in earlier or email it to them.

10:46.000 --> 10:47.680
Since nine months
I am a veteran struggler.

10:51.200 --> 10:52.120
That's me.

10:52.920 --> 10:53.720
Yes.

11:14.800 --> 11:16.840
You can't be tired in
just three or four auditions.

11:16.920 --> 11:18.800
It takes up to three
hundred auditions at times

11:18.920 --> 11:20.200
to finally get a break.

11:23.960 --> 11:24.920
Okay. I'll call you later.

11:25.000 --> 11:25.960
One week is over...

11:26.040 --> 11:27.800
Will you do a lingerie advertisement?

11:27.920 --> 11:28.720
Shomu...

11:28.800 --> 11:33.000
I have told you a million times!
It's lingerie not Lin-guh-ree.

11:33.080 --> 11:34.560
The same thing.
Will you do it?

11:37.600 --> 11:39.840
Meghna won't do such
degrading commercials. Alright?

11:39.920 --> 11:41.040
Why are you getting angry?

11:41.120 --> 11:42.920
What is so degrading in
a lingerie advertisement?

11:43.040 --> 11:44.600
Haven't you seen commercially
successful models in calendars?

11:44.760 --> 11:45.760
They wear whatever they are told.

11:45.840 --> 11:48.160
Attitude walks in before stardom.

11:48.640 --> 11:50.520
And you go to Bandra.
I'll give you an address.

11:50.600 --> 11:51.720
Don't take her seriously.

11:59.400 --> 12:01.760
-We are going for a fashion show tomorrow.
-Fashion show?

12:05.040 --> 12:08.320
Rahul Arora! I have only
seen him on television.

12:08.520 --> 12:12.200
So tomorrow evening it is
Rahul Arora's fashion show. Live!

12:12.280 --> 12:14.520
Honey, I have told you so many times
not to keep your phone switched off.

12:21.400 --> 12:22.280
Not the same thing again!

12:25.160 --> 12:27.440
I should at least know where you are

12:27.520 --> 12:28.680
and what you're up to.

12:33.480 --> 12:34.800
We've been together
for six months.

12:35.120 --> 12:36.560
I know you quite well.

12:41.280 --> 12:42.480
Now what?

12:46.400 --> 12:47.200
For once.

12:56.720 --> 12:57.520
Try to understand.

12:57.960 --> 12:59.200
-Okay, I am hanging up the phone.
-Darling, please.

12:59.280 --> 13:01.520
-We are meeting tonight, right?
-Yes.

13:04.560 --> 13:05.360
Rahul...

13:05.440 --> 13:06.480
Yes, mother.

13:09.960 --> 13:10.960
What can I say?

13:11.680 --> 13:13.200
The whole world is talking.

13:13.760 --> 13:15.960
All those women at temple are now
laughing at me.

13:16.120 --> 13:18.240
They say that I don't want
you to get married.

13:18.320 --> 13:20.200
Let them talk.
How does it affect us?

13:20.280 --> 13:21.800
How can I bear it?

13:21.960 --> 13:23.760
We can't go against society.

13:24.000 --> 13:25.200
It's high time you get married.

13:25.800 --> 13:28.200
Brother Kishen had called from London.

13:28.280 --> 13:30.120
He sent some pictures through email.

13:30.200 --> 13:32.400
Mom! I don't want to see
any pictures of girls.

13:32.480 --> 13:33.800
-At least look at them.
-Mom, please.

13:35.240 --> 13:36.640
Don't bother me at least today.

13:37.440 --> 13:38.800
I have a show tomorrow
and I'm really nervous.

14:04.240 --> 14:05.680
This isn't a garden.

14:05.760 --> 14:07.960
Couturier, lets see it.

14:12.640 --> 14:13.800
Couturier, what is this?

14:14.360 --> 14:15.760
This is the show stopper's outfit.

14:15.840 --> 14:16.840
Increase the length of the slit.

14:17.000 --> 14:18.920
There are only three hours
left for the show.

14:19.000 --> 14:20.520
Please leave.
Don't stress me out.

14:20.760 --> 14:22.040
Please, quickly.

14:22.480 --> 14:25.200
Rahul, pay attention now okay?
We have a run through, alright?

14:25.280 --> 14:26.560
Yes, but where is Shonali?

14:26.840 --> 14:28.640
When is she ever punctual
that today will be an exception?

14:28.720 --> 14:32.040
She is your show stopper
and your favourite.

14:35.720 --> 14:38.000
Why aren't we sitting in the front row?
It's absolutely empty.

14:38.240 --> 14:41.560
Are you nuts?
That's reserved seating, darling.

14:42.040 --> 14:43.920
Just watch what happens
there in a while.

15:23.240 --> 15:24.240
-Meghna.
-Yes?

15:24.360 --> 15:25.200
Look there.

15:25.280 --> 15:26.400
There in the front row...

15:29.480 --> 15:31.400
He is Rahul's biggest rival

15:31.520 --> 15:33.360
and his most loyal audience.

15:33.720 --> 15:35.440
He doesn't miss a single show of Rahul.

15:35.520 --> 15:36.680
And the one sitting there?

15:41.160 --> 15:43.640
There, on right hand corner...

16:05.200 --> 16:08.040
Anisha Roy, the owner
of Profiles Agency.

16:08.120 --> 16:11.760
Every top model since the past
six years is from her agency.

16:23.360 --> 16:26.800
His brand is the biggest
status symbol in the fashion world.

16:27.160 --> 16:29.800
Everyone dances to
his tunes. Everyone.

16:39.240 --> 16:42.480
Charisma

16:42.560 --> 16:44.040
Charisma

16:44.120 --> 16:47.640
Yo blaze up the walk

16:55.720 --> 16:58.080
This is the charisma of bodies

16:58.240 --> 17:00.600
This is the charisma of destiny

17:00.680 --> 17:03.160
Charisma also brings wealth

17:03.320 --> 17:05.680
Charisma also gives us a reason

17:12.480 --> 17:13.520
Charisma

17:15.160 --> 17:16.200
Charisma

17:17.680 --> 17:18.680
Charisma

17:29.800 --> 17:30.800
I'm in the middle of my show.

17:31.080 --> 17:32.920
I told you not to call me.

17:37.120 --> 17:40.960
God knows how many times
you'll break up and patch up.

17:44.720 --> 17:47.920
It flows like fire

17:49.720 --> 17:52.920
It walks in style

17:54.720 --> 17:59.720
It sparks a fire in the hearts

18:00.240 --> 18:01.320
This charisma

18:01.520 --> 18:02.600
This charisma

18:03.000 --> 18:05.080
This is the charisma of fashion

18:05.280 --> 18:07.760
This charisma

18:07.840 --> 18:10.280
This is the charisma of fashion

18:10.680 --> 18:15.480
This is the charisma of fashion

18:15.680 --> 18:20.480
-This is the charisma of fashion
-Okay, go.

18:43.040 --> 18:45.760
The fire

18:48.760 --> 18:51.400
Charisma

18:52.960 --> 18:53.960
Charisma

18:55.440 --> 18:56.480
Charisma

18:58.000 --> 18:59.040
Charisma

19:03.160 --> 19:04.160
Charisma

19:05.720 --> 19:06.720
Charisma

19:14.080 --> 19:19.600
This is the charisma of fashion

19:31.400 --> 19:32.400
Charisma

19:36.600 --> 19:37.600
Charisma

19:39.080 --> 19:40.080
Charisma

19:41.600 --> 19:42.600
Charisma

20:07.160 --> 20:08.440
I spoke to Manish.

20:20.840 --> 20:21.920
She is here to be a model.

20:26.760 --> 20:28.200
She'll dazzle the ramp.

20:37.320 --> 20:39.040
By the way I have my pictures
with me right now.

20:39.200 --> 20:40.200
I'll show you.

20:41.160 --> 20:41.960
Here.

20:53.840 --> 20:56.920
I agree you may not like the pictures
but you need not throw them.

20:57.920 --> 20:59.720
It doesn't look like you have one
in your photographs.

21:02.920 --> 21:05.080
Who would you go to
if you were in my place?

21:05.160 --> 21:07.320
Darling, I wouldn't ever be in your place.

21:15.760 --> 21:18.160
You know Rohit, Kartik is
very busy these days.

21:22.840 --> 21:24.280
I mean look at her.

21:25.840 --> 21:27.600
What difference will
one photo shoot make?

21:27.960 --> 21:29.720
I'm sure if you put in
a word he will agree.

21:32.360 --> 21:36.200
He charges 50,000 rupees,
along with make up and styling.

21:36.520 --> 21:37.600
And separate charges for costumes.

21:38.400 --> 21:39.480
Can she afford it?

21:42.320 --> 21:43.160
But Meghna...

21:46.320 --> 21:47.800
Will 7000 rupees do for now?

21:48.040 --> 21:49.400
I only have that much
with me right now.

21:53.160 --> 21:54.360
I'm making an appointment for

21:54.520 --> 21:56.960
the 20th of next month
at eight in the morning.

21:57.440 --> 21:59.960
If you cancel you forfeit
the advance. Okay?

22:06.480 --> 22:08.280
Manav, I told you earlier as well.

22:09.200 --> 22:11.280
If you want to progress in this industry

22:11.760 --> 22:13.360
you have to compromise.

22:14.800 --> 22:17.440
Do you think that
all the successful models

22:17.520 --> 22:19.760
found work just like that?

22:22.160 --> 22:23.480
They also had to compromise.

22:25.480 --> 22:28.280
I can't do what others do.

22:30.200 --> 22:32.120
I want to be successful
on my own terms.

22:33.040 --> 22:34.080
Not like this.

22:51.240 --> 22:53.040
I am speaking from
Vinay Khosla's office, ma'am.

22:53.400 --> 22:55.560
I'm here with your
outfits for the trial.

23:02.360 --> 23:04.520
What are you doing here?
Did you have a meeting?

23:04.600 --> 23:07.040
Yes, kind of.

23:08.120 --> 23:10.080
That's what I came here for,
but it didn't work out.

23:23.920 --> 23:25.320
You should have at least
introduced me to him.

23:27.080 --> 23:27.920
Rohit.

23:29.760 --> 23:32.440
-Now what?
-Lunch.

23:33.280 --> 23:37.120
Enjoy, Meghna.
I only have mineral water.

23:37.680 --> 23:40.400
Especially when someone
else is paying the bill.

23:40.520 --> 23:44.240
But how can we eat out here?
It's so expensive.

23:45.880 --> 23:49.000
Mrs. Agarwal is an NRI.
She is very rich.

23:49.200 --> 23:53.600
She told me to have lunch
and add the bill to her account.

23:54.600 --> 23:55.840
Shomu had called up.

23:55.920 --> 23:56.920
-What?
-Yes.

23:57.160 --> 24:00.320
She said there is
a party at some hotel.

24:00.640 --> 24:02.840
If I want to make contacts,
I must go.

24:03.520 --> 24:04.320
Should I go?

24:06.280 --> 24:07.960
Networking is very important.

24:08.360 --> 24:09.920
What fun!

24:10.960 --> 24:13.400
Lunch and dinner both
at a five star hotel.

24:27.880 --> 24:29.720
Stop fooling around.

24:30.240 --> 24:32.320
The girls have been waiting in
the lobby since long.

24:32.720 --> 24:36.160
Listen, there are three girls.
One of them is new.

24:36.480 --> 24:38.760
Explain it to all of them properly.
Got it?

24:39.200 --> 24:41.240
Yes, I'll be there in five minutes.

24:42.840 --> 24:44.400
Sorry, Sameer.
I have to go.

24:49.760 --> 24:51.560
Not Sameer, Janet.
My name is Sohail.

24:56.360 --> 24:58.280
Stay together everybody. Okay?

24:58.680 --> 25:00.040
Where is Bajaj?

25:21.680 --> 25:23.320
The "Kanta laga" type.

25:52.640 --> 25:53.800
No, thank you. I don't drink.

25:54.920 --> 25:58.760
Drink up. It's free and imported too.

26:00.480 --> 26:04.120
Shomu said that I could
make some contacts here.

26:04.360 --> 26:06.680
-Drink ma'am.
-Contacts? And that too here?

26:08.200 --> 26:12.520
Just smile and look pretty
for the photographs.

26:13.160 --> 26:15.600
And then our job is done.
That's it!

26:38.960 --> 26:41.080
No, not as yet but hopefully...

26:42.840 --> 26:45.240
Send me some of your photographs.

26:45.320 --> 26:47.560
I suggest that you
drop in to my office.

26:56.880 --> 26:58.160
Janet, Meet Mr...

26:58.240 --> 27:01.360
-Mukesh Tyagi. He runs an ad agency.
-Yes.

27:06.760 --> 27:08.040
He says he has a lot of contacts.

27:08.280 --> 27:10.800
I've been meeting him in parties
since the past five years.

27:11.960 --> 27:13.160
Listen, fraud.

27:13.240 --> 27:17.200
You won't catch any fish with such tricks.
Go from here.

27:20.200 --> 27:22.280
What's the problem with
you small town girls?

27:23.200 --> 27:26.120
Anyone who speaks halfway decent English,
can get anywhere with you.

27:26.600 --> 27:27.600
Come on, let's go.

27:27.720 --> 27:28.840
"Want to make contacts."

27:35.240 --> 27:39.240
Dolly, that's your 15,000 rupees.
I've cut 5000 rupees for the advance.

27:39.320 --> 27:40.720
-There are 10,000 rupees in the packet.
-Okay, fine.

27:40.960 --> 27:41.960
And here's your 18,000 rupees.

27:42.160 --> 27:43.200
Don't ask for conveyance.

27:43.560 --> 27:45.560
We've got a party like this
after a month. Got it?

27:48.080 --> 27:49.320
And Meghna...

27:49.680 --> 27:51.640
It's your first time so
I'm paying you 12,000 rupees.

27:53.000 --> 27:55.120
What are you looking at?
Here take it.

27:55.720 --> 27:56.560
Don't you want it?

27:56.920 --> 27:59.560
But money for what?

28:00.120 --> 28:02.520
You're paid for the work you did.

28:03.080 --> 28:04.560
Work?

28:04.760 --> 28:06.680
Didn't you pose for the camera?

28:07.240 --> 28:10.000
People like having girls
at such parties.

28:10.360 --> 28:12.920
Mr. Bajaj is an event manager.

28:13.040 --> 28:14.720
He contacts me for the models.

28:15.320 --> 28:16.320
It's like

28:16.400 --> 28:19.240
pretty girls get the glamor
quotient for such parties.

28:19.840 --> 28:21.880
High society calls this
eye candy, understood?

28:21.960 --> 28:22.960
Now take it.

28:23.400 --> 28:24.320
