with flowers, to a proud mother.

1:45:09.680 --> 1:45:13.480
Meghna, your reckless behaviour is
not only damaging your reputation...

1:45:13.920 --> 1:45:15.440
but Panache's too.

1:45:16.200 --> 1:45:17.320
I know you are upset.

1:45:17.840 --> 1:45:21.320
But learn to keep your personal life
apart from your professional life.

1:45:29.240 --> 1:45:30.240
Tell me something, Abhi.

1:45:31.920 --> 1:45:32.920
What about our relationship?

1:45:35.440 --> 1:45:36.800
Is it personal or professional?

1:46:22.320 --> 1:46:24.200
I am telling you, they don't
want to sell the food there.

1:47:03.600 --> 1:47:05.720
I think you have taken
my words too seriously.

1:47:07.000 --> 1:47:08.280
You have become so professional

1:47:08.360 --> 1:47:09.760
that you are uneasy greeting me.

1:47:22.280 --> 1:47:23.760
Mrs. Sarin.

1:47:26.040 --> 1:47:28.280
I saw all that drama on television.

1:47:34.560 --> 1:47:35.640
Didn't you tell her?

1:47:39.720 --> 1:47:40.680
I was in a clinic.

1:47:47.960 --> 1:47:49.880
Abhi will give you the details.

1:47:51.760 --> 1:47:54.000
After all he paid the bill.

1:48:03.120 --> 1:48:05.200
Oh! She got offended.

1:48:16.680 --> 1:48:18.560
I'm telling you again Meghna,
it's still not too late.

1:48:19.160 --> 1:48:21.120
Avantika is very upset.

1:48:23.840 --> 1:48:26.560
Just meet her once and apologise.

1:48:26.640 --> 1:48:28.760
If she forgives you,
everything will be sorted.

1:48:28.840 --> 1:48:29.840
I should apologise to her?

1:48:34.280 --> 1:48:35.680
Who is she, Anisha?

1:48:40.600 --> 1:48:41.680
I don't need her.

1:48:42.560 --> 1:48:45.400
Of course, you need her, Meghna.

1:48:46.240 --> 1:48:48.600
You're in this position due to Panache.

1:48:48.760 --> 1:48:50.560
All the brands are signing you.

1:48:58.560 --> 1:49:02.920
I don't need Panache,
Panache needs me. Okay?

1:49:08.840 --> 1:49:09.840
Anything else?

1:49:49.120 --> 1:49:50.120
I just read the paper.

1:49:52.640 --> 1:49:53.960
This had to happen.

1:49:54.200 --> 1:49:55.400
I told you so.

1:49:57.720 --> 1:49:59.520
Gauri Anand is from your agency.

1:49:59.600 --> 1:50:02.360
That means you knew I was
going to be replaced!

1:50:10.360 --> 1:50:11.720
Aren't you ashamed of yourself?

1:50:13.400 --> 1:50:16.400
When we replaced Shonali...

1:50:17.080 --> 1:50:18.800
you didn't ask me this.

1:50:35.080 --> 1:50:36.840
The sound of a shattered
dream never hurts

1:50:36.920 --> 1:50:38.840
as much as it's lasting echo.

1:50:40.000 --> 1:50:42.640
My career started falling
like a pack of cards

1:50:42.720 --> 1:50:44.680
and I stood there,
like a mere spectator.

1:50:45.320 --> 1:50:47.480
Everything changed.
Home, relationships...

1:50:47.560 --> 1:50:48.960
and along with them I changed too.

1:50:49.920 --> 1:50:52.400
Commitments, sincerity, professionalism...

1:50:52.800 --> 1:50:55.480
I ran away from all of them

1:50:55.680 --> 1:50:59.080
and reached a place so loud...

1:50:59.280 --> 1:51:02.160
that I couldn't even hear myself.

1:51:03.280 --> 1:51:07.800
What I was doing, why I was doing it...
I had no clue at all.

1:51:08.720 --> 1:51:12.960
Shonali was right,
I couldn't even recognize myself.

1:51:22.560 --> 1:51:24.000
You've had a lot to drink.

1:51:25.480 --> 1:51:26.920
You're saying this, Janet!

1:51:29.800 --> 1:51:31.920
Look, I don't know how to lecture.

1:51:32.280 --> 1:51:35.080
But I can say that
you're ruining yourself.

1:51:36.680 --> 1:51:39.800
You don't know how to lecture,
so please don't try.

1:51:41.320 --> 1:51:45.080
Meghna, everyone I meet is
talking about your arrogance.

1:51:49.040 --> 1:51:51.480
It's important to have an
attitude to be successful.

1:51:55.200 --> 1:51:56.960
Is that necessary too?

1:51:58.720 --> 1:52:01.640
Listen, if you continue to behave like
this no one will want to work with you.

1:52:12.080 --> 1:52:14.200
What do you know
about professionalism?

1:52:15.680 --> 1:52:18.920
You don't become a model by doing
a couple of small assignments.

1:52:22.400 --> 1:52:25.920
Listen, I know I didn't make it big.

1:52:26.320 --> 1:52:29.400
But I have spent more
time in this industry.

1:52:31.680 --> 1:52:34.680
I know why your reputation
is getting ruined.

1:52:35.320 --> 1:52:36.920
That's why I'm telling you.

1:52:37.120 --> 1:52:39.280
Straighten up before everything crumbles.

1:52:43.040 --> 1:52:44.080
Straighten up?

1:52:45.640 --> 1:52:46.680
How?

1:52:47.880 --> 1:52:50.280
Should I beg Sarin or Anisha?

1:52:52.760 --> 1:52:54.360
I know what I can do.

1:52:55.760 --> 1:52:59.160
I should marry a rich
gay designer like you.

1:53:28.280 --> 1:53:29.360
Hi, babes. Where are you?

1:53:32.160 --> 1:53:34.000
Yes, I'll be there.

1:53:36.640 --> 1:53:41.320
Charisma

1:53:45.080 --> 1:53:49.960
Charisma

1:53:52.240 --> 1:53:56.160
It's the charisma of the bodies

1:53:56.320 --> 1:53:58.520
Charisma also brings wealth

1:53:58.600 --> 1:54:00.640
Charisma also gives us a reason

1:54:04.880 --> 1:54:08.800
Charisma feels adorable

1:54:08.880 --> 1:54:16.840
It's enjoyment
It's intoxication

1:54:18.560 --> 1:54:26.360
Charisma
It flows like fire and walks in style

1:54:27.600 --> 1:54:31.880
It sparks a fire in the hearts

1:54:32.040 --> 1:54:36.240
This is the charisma of fashion

1:54:36.320 --> 1:54:40.400
This is the charisma of fashion

1:54:40.480 --> 1:54:44.440
This is the charisma of fashion

1:54:44.640 --> 1:54:48.640
This is the charisma of fashion

1:55:22.360 --> 1:55:26.160
It has distracted everyone
Its illusion is unique

1:55:26.600 --> 1:55:30.720
No one escape from this charisma

1:55:30.800 --> 1:55:34.440
It also shows you the sky and
Brings you down on the Earth

1:55:34.520 --> 1:55:36.560
It has made us do everything for it

1:55:36.640 --> 1:55:38.480
This charisma

1:55:38.560 --> 1:55:41.960
It flows like fire

1:55:43.040 --> 1:55:45.040
It walks in style

1:55:47.200 --> 1:55:51.080
It sparks a fire in the hearts

1:55:51.520 --> 1:55:55.400
This is the charisma of fashion

1:55:55.880 --> 1:55:59.840
This is the charisma of fashion

1:55:59.960 --> 1:56:04.200
This is the charisma of fashion

1:56:04.280 --> 1:56:08.240
This is the charisma of fashion

2:00:35.760 --> 2:00:36.800
Meghna...

2:00:42.680 --> 2:00:43.680
Dear...

2:01:01.000 --> 2:01:03.240
We become totally isolated

2:01:04.120 --> 2:01:05.840
when we lose our own company.

2:01:07.400 --> 2:01:09.000
I came back home to Chandigarh...

2:01:09.960 --> 2:01:12.040
but I could never be myself.

2:01:13.000 --> 2:01:14.760
Leaving all my relationships behind

2:01:15.200 --> 2:01:17.600
I descended into my inner darkness.

2:01:18.880 --> 2:01:21.800
I neither felt happy nor sad.

2:01:26.680 --> 2:01:29.080
The psychiatrist advised...

2:01:29.240 --> 2:01:32.040
that nothing is possible until

2:01:32.120 --> 2:01:37.840
I rediscover myself and
my self-confidence.

2:01:39.240 --> 2:01:42.400
But as easy as it is to lose oneself...

2:01:42.480 --> 2:01:45.560
it is even more difficult
to forgive...

2:01:46.600 --> 2:01:48.440
and find oneself again.

2:01:50.440 --> 2:01:52.120
Have you heard anything about Shonali?

2:01:53.680 --> 2:01:55.560
I heard that she's in some rehab.

2:01:56.960 --> 2:01:58.000
No one knows where exactly.

2:02:07.360 --> 2:02:09.480
Who is your show stopper
for the Delhi show?

2:02:10.200 --> 2:02:13.880
I heard that just like Vinay Khosla,
you too have roped in a film star.

2:02:16.520 --> 2:02:18.880
But if there was a model

2:02:19.120 --> 2:02:21.080
for a show stopper for
this show, that's best.

2:03:11.040 --> 2:03:12.080
Meghna.

2:03:17.200 --> 2:03:18.000
Dear...

2:03:20.080 --> 2:03:21.760
The one who loses...

2:03:22.840 --> 2:03:24.160
isn't the one who falls.

2:03:25.920 --> 2:03:27.160
But a failure is one...

2:03:28.080 --> 2:03:29.680
who still doesn't rise to the occasion.

2:03:31.240 --> 2:03:33.920
My daughter is not a loser.

2:03:36.840 --> 2:03:37.920
I'm sorry, my dear.

2:03:41.760 --> 2:03:43.280
It was my fault.

2:03:45.520 --> 2:03:48.240
That I didn't trust my daughter's dream...

2:03:49.280 --> 2:03:51.720
-and how high it could take her.
-Papa...

2:03:54.960 --> 2:03:56.880
I had trust in my daughter...

2:03:57.320 --> 2:03:58.480
and I still do.

2:04:01.400 --> 2:04:05.720
Meghna, go ahead and
pursue your dream again.

2:04:07.520 --> 2:04:08.520
Yes, my dear.

2:04:14.400 --> 2:04:15.480
Go back, my dear.

2:04:23.080 --> 2:04:24.080
Yes, dear.

2:04:26.760 --> 2:04:28.680
Go back, my dear.

2:04:59.480 --> 2:05:02.200
I thought I'd come and apologise.

2:05:06.000 --> 2:05:07.200
But I can't.

2:05:22.760 --> 2:05:25.600
But when I decided to come back...

2:05:27.200 --> 2:05:29.200
I couldn't think of anyone else but you.

2:05:34.040 --> 2:05:35.160
So, I came right here.

2:05:41.360 --> 2:05:42.720
Didn't I do the right thing, Janet?

2:06:06.880 --> 2:06:09.920
You may borrow clothes for
a function, but do return them.

2:06:48.120 --> 2:06:49.880
She's sent it to everyone.

2:06:57.280 --> 2:06:59.600
You know, she always
compared herself to Shonali.

2:07:00.760 --> 2:07:02.840
Mark my words, someday
she will lose it just like Shonali.

2:08:18.680 --> 2:08:20.360
You went through a lot in your life.

2:08:24.280 --> 2:08:25.880
But the good thing is
that you have come back.

2:08:40.680 --> 2:08:42.600
I know I've hurt you a lot.

2:08:46.320 --> 2:08:50.600
I'm really happy for you that
today you're in the big league.

2:09:09.120 --> 2:09:10.440
We got engaged last month.

2:09:18.520 --> 2:09:20.080
-No.
-Please stay for a while.

2:09:20.680 --> 2:09:21.560
Some other time.

2:09:56.080 --> 2:09:59.920
It is said that the people you meet
on your way up to success...

2:10:00.360 --> 2:10:03.840
you encounter them again
on your way down.

2:10:06.800 --> 2:10:08.640
It felt really weird.

2:10:11.160 --> 2:10:15.280
The relations I left behind in
arrogance of my success...

2:10:15.360 --> 2:10:20.200
have left me and gone way ahead in life.

2:10:21.400 --> 2:10:22.640
Everything had changed.

2:10:24.520 --> 2:10:27.800
But thank God.
Some relationships in life...

2:10:28.240 --> 2:10:31.400
don't require an
invitation for acceptance.

2:10:51.640 --> 2:10:52.840
For giving me this show.

2:10:54.920 --> 2:10:56.680
I know that you didn't have to do it.

2:10:59.080 --> 2:11:01.720
And everyone must have
advised you not to.

2:11:03.840 --> 2:11:05.480
No one knows you like I do.

2:11:05.920 --> 2:11:09.280
Look, if I could have my way,
you would be my show stopper.

2:11:17.040 --> 2:11:19.720
The fact that I'm even in
your show, means a lot.

2:11:23.400 --> 2:11:27.280
After all, it is my first show
on comeback and...

2:12:02.640 --> 2:12:05.080
Daisy, why isn't the dress ironed yet?

2:12:12.880 --> 2:12:14.480
-Meghna...
-Hi.

2:12:14.720 --> 2:12:15.720
Meghna, are you okay?

2:12:15.800 --> 2:12:16.800
Yes, of course.

2:15:27.080 --> 2:15:28.800
I froze on the head ramp.

2:15:33.000 --> 2:15:34.160
It happens sometimes, Meghna.

2:15:36.320 --> 2:15:37.320
It doesn't happen, Rahul.

2:15:47.880 --> 2:15:49.280
You were nervous then, that's all.

2:15:49.920 --> 2:15:51.800
I mean, you walked
the ramp after a year.

2:15:52.040 --> 2:15:55.440
Meghna just think!
How will your dad feel?

2:16:08.120 --> 2:16:09.480
You know how this industry works.

2:16:10.240 --> 2:16:13.040
There is no room for weakness.

2:16:30.640 --> 2:16:31.640
Yes, that's her.

2:16:31.960 --> 2:16:33.360
What has she done to her?

2:16:36.760 --> 2:16:39.040
-Madam, do you know anybody here?
-Shut up! Go away!

2:16:39.120 --> 2:16:41.879
Madam, please tell us.
Do you know anyone here?

2:16:51.240 --> 2:16:53.600
People say that she has
been here for the last two days

2:16:53.680 --> 2:16:55.280
and isn't talking to anyone.

2:16:55.559 --> 2:16:57.480
Shonali Gujral's distressing story...

2:16:58.000 --> 2:17:01.160
highlights another truth
of the fashion industry.

2:17:01.240 --> 2:17:04.959
It is evident that the profession
isn't as glamorous as it seems.

2:17:05.240 --> 2:17:09.200
It is said that she ran away from rehab.

2:17:21.719 --> 2:17:22.920
Listen, Inspector...

2:17:23.080 --> 2:17:24.440
instead of roaming
on the streets...

2:17:24.600 --> 2:17:27.080
instead of making a mockery
in front of the media...

2:17:27.160 --> 2:17:29.080
it is better that
we take her along.

2:17:29.200 --> 2:17:31.480
Our NGO will
take good care of her.

2:17:31.879 --> 2:17:33.120
Madam, it's a procedure.

2:17:33.400 --> 2:17:35.040
Until her family members don't come...

2:17:35.200 --> 2:17:36.799
and don't take her along...

2:17:37.320 --> 2:17:38.840
or she doesn't say anything...

2:17:39.120 --> 2:17:40.920
we can't let you take her.

2:17:49.360 --> 2:17:51.120
Madam, do you know her?

2:17:53.520 --> 2:17:54.520
Yes, I do.

2:18:06.480 --> 2:18:09.240
Meghna, it's a huge responsibility.

2:18:09.879 --> 2:18:11.080
You yourself are struggling.

2:18:11.680 --> 2:18:13.799
Can you afford to look
after her as well?

2:18:17.840 --> 2:18:20.719
I haven't thought about it, Janet.

2:18:23.200 --> 2:18:24.360
All I know is...

2:18:26.160 --> 2:18:27.440
I'm not doing it for Shonali...

2:18:29.040 --> 2:18:30.080
but for myself.

2:18:55.400 --> 2:18:58.799
After bringing Shonali
home I realized

2:18:58.879 --> 2:19:02.040
that our lives were quite similar.

2:19:03.680 --> 2:19:05.520
Both of us had lost ourselves.

2:19:07.080 --> 2:19:09.080
The happiness I achieved in helping...

2:19:09.680 --> 2:19:11.520
Shonali come back to a normal life...

2:19:11.879 --> 2:19:15.559
was more important than the happiness
of professional success.

2:19:16.799 --> 2:19:23.440
As she got better, I regained
the self confidence I had lost.

2:20:00.840 --> 2:20:02.440
In fact everything was
finalized yesterday.

2:20:06.720 --> 2:20:07.720
Who is the show stopper?

2:20:08.160 --> 2:20:09.360
Like Vinay Khosla's...

2:20:15.760 --> 2:20:17.240
Ms. Meghna Mathur.

2:20:29.680 --> 2:20:31.520
After what happened
at Rohit's show...

2:20:34.280 --> 2:20:37.680
Meghna, we've given
this a lot of thought.

2:20:43.400 --> 2:20:45.440
I know you'll are doing this for me.

2:20:46.000 --> 2:20:48.760
And I appreciate it. I really do.
I am really grateful, but...

2:21:01.720 --> 2:21:03.320
Why don't you want to do the show?

2:21:05.800 --> 2:21:09.480
You do know how important
this show is for you, don't you?

2:21:10.200 --> 2:21:11.400
Come on, Shonali.

2:21:12.600 --> 2:21:14.600
You do know what happened
during Rohit's show and...

2:21:18.240 --> 2:21:19.840
This show is very
important for Rahul.

2:21:28.920 --> 2:21:30.560
Meghna, you aren't
worried for Rahul...

2:21:31.440 --> 2:21:33.040
but you're afraid of failing again.

2:21:35.800 --> 2:21:37.960
Rahul has so much confidence in you.

2:21:38.880 --> 2:21:40.520
Isn't it your turn...

2:21:41.520 --> 2:21:43.800
to prove him right?

2:21:55.640 --> 2:21:57.680
We have lost a lot here, Meghna.

2:22:03.800 --> 2:22:08.080
But if this show helps
you make a comeback...

2:22:30.040 --> 2:22:32.080
I have never interfered
in your decisions, Rahul.

2:22:32.680 --> 2:22:33.720
So why do it now?

2:22:35.280 --> 2:22:37.800
To make Meghna the show stopper
for such an important show!

2:22:39.680 --> 2:22:41.880
And you know
what she did at Rohit's show.

2:22:49.720 --> 2:22:52.360
People from the Paris Fashion
Week are coming to see the finale.

2:22:52.960 --> 2:22:56.160
If there is any problem in this show
then Paris is out of the question.

2:23:05.320 --> 2:23:06.360
Nothing of that sort will happen.

2:23:07.760 --> 2:23:09.800
But is it necessary to take
such a big risk for this show?

2:23:10.200 --> 2:23:12.120
There are other shows as well.
Give her a chance there.

2:23:12.480 --> 2:23:14.240
No, Abhijeet. It'll be too late then.

2:23:45.200 --> 2:23:47.760
The Kimaya Fashion Week
has begun with a controversy.

2:23:48.320 --> 2:23:50.480
Bollywood's ace
designer Vinay Khosla...

2:23:50.720 --> 2:23:55.040
has accused upcoming designer
Zulfi Khan with stealing his designs.

2:23:57.800 --> 2:24:00.680
I had designed them for a film,
which he has stolen from there.

2:24:01.000 --> 2:24:02.960
I can show you the DVD.

2:24:14.840 --> 2:24:15.640
Yes.

2:24:16.200 --> 2:24:18.960
Rohit's driver will come
to pick you up from the airport.

2:24:19.040 --> 2:24:21.600
-Come directly to the venue.
-Okay. Did you have dinner?

2:24:21.680 --> 2:24:23.600
No, mom. I have just returned
from a fitting session.

2:24:23.880 --> 2:24:26.120
Okay, dear. Take care of yourself.

2:24:26.200 --> 2:24:27.160
We will be there.

2:24:38.520 --> 2:24:39.520
Shonali!

2:24:49.200 --> 2:24:50.200
Shonali?

2:24:56.560 --> 2:24:57.560
Shonali!

2:25:11.560 --> 2:25:12.640
Shonali...

2:25:32.120 --> 2:25:34.640
Janet, Shonali isn't at home.

2:25:34.720 --> 2:25:36.440
The house is a mess.
I don't know what to do!

2:25:38.440 --> 2:25:39.520
-What is it?
-We'll be there soon.

2:25:48.680 --> 2:25:49.720
Who are these people?

2:26:01.200 --> 2:26:02.200
Did she come here?

2:26:03.160 --> 2:26:04.160
Why would she come here?

2:26:06.080 --> 2:26:08.040
She hasn't paid me 5,000 rupees
for the stuff as yet.

2:26:08.520 --> 2:26:09.800
She's probably lying
around on the streets.

2:26:19.480 --> 2:26:20.600
What did he say?

2:26:20.760 --> 2:26:22.040
Shinde, pay attention.

2:26:22.360 --> 2:26:24.680
If you get any information,
call immediately.

2:26:25.400 --> 2:26:27.000
Look, don't panic.

2:26:27.960 --> 2:26:30.200
We've sent out a search party.

2:26:30.640 --> 2:26:32.160
We'll try our best.

2:26:32.360 --> 2:26:34.280
We have your number.

2:26:36.600 --> 2:26:38.760
If we get any information about Shonali

2:26:39.160 --> 2:26:40.160
we will inform you.

2:26:40.280 --> 2:26:42.080
-But...
-Relax.

2:26:42.680 --> 2:26:44.720
Sir, please try your best.

2:27:18.400 --> 2:27:20.000
Don't worry.
We'll find Shonali.

2:27:20.280 --> 2:27:21.680
We've informed the police.

2:27:22.200 --> 2:27:23.280
Everything will be alright.

2:28:21.800 --> 2:28:23.000
Alicia.

2:28:37.320 --> 2:28:39.520
I have been tantalizing you

2:28:39.840 --> 2:28:42.800
